title: Nine To Noon - 3/2 Nordo in for PA... Kevin Falness, and Aaron Gleeman join
description: Falness joins to break down the heartbreaker last night in the Vegas desert as the Wild drop their first game in their last 7 in OT after surrendering a 2-goal 3rd PD lead... Plus, Aaron Gleeman joins us in studio to break down Twins and Wolves
